<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_396cb0f6-6ff5-49da-9c51-d4ba94a22e79" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>D4D2</sptc><title id="_e9d0a7af-b525-449d-adaa-52cf50c253b8">General building access requirements</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_4d6a00ad-572d-47cc-a60b-6a0f41f98e91" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_1069f439-521e-4458-a556-ec10e71a7f44">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Buildings and parts of buildings must be <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_643d8563-2919-4525-8ca4-355944830b1f" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> as <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_6602218a-6736-4a94-9a1a-951426792326" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by this clause, unless exempted by <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2045_1.3.0.xml#_568558a9-8fff-4f9f-8bc1-98ef597c74d7" id="_06d1c7df-af8b-485e-af3d-8313d019ee25" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="clause">D4D5</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_f1eb765b-2b28-4082-8dc0-3c32f17b6a90" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_817d926b-1e4d-44a1-9204-960eb8f58ce8">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Access requirements for a Class 1b building are as follows:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_0de453dd-2d23-4bc4-a8c0-fe40a6866b41">Dwellings located on one allotment and used for short-term holiday accommodation — to and within a number of dwellings determined in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/34_1.1.0.xml#_e1aaf424-bb3a-490a-b431-8aace1ebca04" id="_50179dfd-a875-49ce-967d-b0c587519310" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table D4D2a</xref>.</li><li id="_9256962e-a082-463c-b670-e92891f5d9a5">A boarding house, bed and breakfast, guest house, hostel or the like, other than those described in (a) — to and within—<ol><li>one bedroom and associated sanitary facilities; and</li><li>not less than one of each type of room or space for use in common by the residents or guests, including a cooking facility, sauna, gymnasium, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_dbe114c5-854f-4959-992e-e27ffabdce8c" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, laundry, games room, eating area, or the like; and</li><li>rooms or spaces for use in common by all residents on a floor to which access by way of a ramp complying with AS 1428.1 or a passenger lift is provided.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_143e2caf-64ad-412f-97f6-4b70a5696d61" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_29994021-9c35-460c-982d-66b0cf5c11cc">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>For the purposes of (2)(a), a community or strata-type subdivision or development is considered to be on a single allotment.</p></subclause><subclause id="_0697babe-2582-4026-8c29-164edfe0de7b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cda60783-f279-40ae-922d-59ab7da133b6">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>For a Class 2 building, common areas are to be <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_4c564504-5d6f-4e19-b843-508aea9cf817" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> as follows:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_40424963-1db7-4682-9aed-95266eeb5ed4">From a pedestrian entrance <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_c316c87c-fca8-4b02-b6fb-f5c4a0568460" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_647ede5c-c367-4d19-98fe-8692443348fd" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> to at least one floor containing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_db385ebb-8635-49a2-9111-92bae4da2ce9" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy units</xref> and to the entrance doorway of each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_e504b212-57c2-4aca-8453-6cc146b31b7e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> located on that level.</li><li id="_937eb0b2-1f50-43e8-90e0-1497baba4ff8">To and within not less than one of each type of room or space for use in common by the residents, including a cooking facility, sauna, gymnasium, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_e8433710-37e3-4227-a710-1d1bc775afaa" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, common laundry, games room, individual shop, eating area, or the like.</li><li id="_b34963ab-7fec-4eec-b239-809bf174d3d3">Where a ramp complying with AS 1428.1 or a passenger lift is installed—<ol><li>to the entrance doorway of each <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_04748951-9499-48d5-a43a-d3aba4e793aa" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref>; and</li><li>to and within rooms or spaces for use in common by the residents.</li></ol></li><li id="_99af77d8-a75d-488d-a5d4-7f632bacfe7a">The requirements of (c) only apply where the space referred to in (c)(i) or (ii) is located on the levels served by the lift or ramp.</li></ol><subclause id="_cfd19ea2-ed3a-4b7c-af32-86deccf9a362" outputclass="state-variation" variation="SA" variation-type="REPLACE"><title id="_376156b4-07a1-4f88-a0c3-30ab123db9a7">SA REPLACE SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>For a Class 2 building, access requirements are as follows:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_36ce5c66-f56b-4310-8fd3-d3a1b3868edf">Common areas:<ol outputclass="alpha"><li>From a pedestrian entrance <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_89170c08-f83e-489a-a3fb-056f883538d3" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_3b337d93-0d20-43ea-abb5-20a68edbe234" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> to at least one floor containing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_90fcc0a7-5a08-45db-bc0f-5bc8a51b8c40" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy units</xref> and to the entrance doorway of each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_a8a94190-9b05-47da-bc18-3b155ad8dee7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> located on that level.</li><li>To and within not less than one of each type of room or space for use in common by the residents, including a cooking facility, sauna, gymnasium, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_51c0448d-12d2-4705-b23a-bb175fc60dcf" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, common laundry, games room, individual shop, eating area, or the like.</li><li>Where a ramp complying with AS 1428.1 or a passenger lift is installed—<ol><li>to the entrance doorway of each <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_5051292a-74c6-4ab7-ae1e-cd4782c892d7" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref>; and</li><li>to and within rooms or spaces for use in common by the residents.</li></ol></li><li>The requirements of (iii) only apply where the space referred to in (iii)(A) or (iii)(B) is located on the levels served by the lift or ramp.</li></ol></li><li id="_68c46dc8-6268-457a-9617-8d42ddaa9354">In developments consisting of 20 or more residential <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_396dad9c-9716-401d-a9b0-befdf6a933c9" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy units</xref> — to and within one residential <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_6ff34f8d-7a85-46a9-bf73-ea248bf9da62" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> or 5% of the total number of residential <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_cf56aa34-cb89-4da8-a212-d24ad50332a4" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy units</xref> provided, whichever is the greater, must be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_0f7629af-405c-4653-b2c0-c72edc064e06" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></subclause><subclause id="_20830f39-df7b-4321-a5c0-19b267e91c65" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_f5882b91-de49-4bc0-8cc1-6711b253559e">SubClause</title><num>5</num><p>For a Class 3 building, access requirements are as follows:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_12f77953-41b3-4df2-ba49-c98d86e1dc9e">Common areas:<ol><li>From a pedestrian entrance <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_c3a9ee90-1414-4d9e-8e6c-507b02229783" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_bc7c61f2-1637-4828-bfcb-78c142f00186" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> to at least one floor containing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_2ed613d0-b229-4715-86c7-e4ab1bae4553" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy units</xref> and to the entrance doorway of each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_ce88fc6c-2a04-440d-8c0d-788f4c9f713d" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> located on that level.</li><li>To and within not less than one of each type of room or space for use in common by the residents, including a cooking facility, sauna, gymnasium, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_3f9ebc61-0bf4-4678-aa63-854d924c08e6" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, common laundry, games room, TV room, individual shop, dining room, public viewing area, ticket purchasing service, lunch room, lounge room, or the like.</li><li>Where a ramp complying with AS 1428.1 or a passenger lift is installed—<ol><li>to the entrance doorway of each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_6041d559-55fe-481a-8d81-7224228997d2" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref>; and</li><li>to and within rooms or spaces for use in common by the residents.</li></ol></li><li>The requirements of (iii) only apply where the space referred to in (iii)(A) or (iii)(B) is located on the levels served by the lift or ramp.</li></ol></li><li id="_c5b2ea42-fbdf-4afb-bfa0-9dec0a7d07e4">To and within <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_2c60ce55-5ad0-41f7-a691-f0a2f74f07f8" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy units</xref> — in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/37_1.4.0.xml#_118a8046-d884-4cc9-baa8-75574a067127" id="_58f2fe4a-ded4-4626-8886-558c9bd9d355" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table D4D2b</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_f34a5287-64f4-4693-87d0-19a031a4300e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_5892b288-a656-4098-b673-2cc988cb157a">SubClause</title><num>6</num><p>For Class 5, 6, 7b, 8 and 9a buildings, access must be provided to and within all areas normally used by the occupants.</p></subclause><subclause id="_6b350735-369c-4609-aeb2-5a96d7018ed6" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_366003b1-6f6f-451f-941f-3aed4cd63509">SubClause</title><num>7</num><p>For a Class 7a building, access must be provided to and within any level containing <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_0c10aba3-530e-4226-b9b0-da3cf64eaa74" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> carparking spaces.</p></subclause><subclause id="_6a50399b-bda5-431e-b009-e27ad7380caf" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cd2f9cba-a356-40b9-aa04-88109f08fbca">SubClause</title><num>8</num><p>For a Class 9b building, access requirements are as follows:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_eea3f3eb-b71d-48ab-bcf3-8a8c0b81d333"><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1447_0.6.0.xml#_23515733-4511-421a-8c89-650d33e5f6e4" id="_a04167f4-cca2-492d-bc53-18d081290509" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">Schools</xref> and <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1251_2.4.0.xml#_9ff8fad7-8992-4708-be17-784d962a0530" id="_96c15769-b25a-4d3c-8850-c8079f4f3d61" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">early childhood centres</xref> — to and within all areas normally used by the occupants.</li><li id="_290971e4-0831-438b-9f8f-7bdf56204215">An <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1195_1.0.0.xml#_367d20c3-85f7-45e8-ad37-bba3e069f07d" id="_c930843d-b67c-4a81-b90a-9741014ed6fc" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">assembly building</xref>, not being a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1447_0.6.0.xml#_23515733-4511-421a-8c89-650d33e5f6e4" id="_b65a6ae3-3c40-480e-a5fd-77a817dd531f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">school</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1251_2.4.0.xml#_9ff8fad7-8992-4708-be17-784d962a0530" id="_daf23624-f472-40e2-91b4-1967ccab5b06" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">early childhood centre</xref> — to and within— <ol><li>wheelchair seating spaces provided in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2055_1.3.0.xml#_cb606408-59d5-41df-99f2-67f767661ad4" id="_3bc67439-d5da-4ad3-aa21-e06b79de6aa4" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D4D10</xref>; and</li><li>all other areas normally used by the occupants, except that access need not be provided to tiers or platforms of seating areas that do not contain wheelchair seating spaces.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_0fcb1fa1-c81d-4cc4-a10b-8f7c2919c19d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c6e6e2bf-7107-4e4c-971f-7b671b4d9123">SubClause</title><num>9</num><p>For a Class 9c building, access requirements are as follows:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_6835bb9c-1aa3-4cf4-be8d-9a6517c84c52">Common areas:<ol><li>From a pedestrian entrance <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_e42e2978-cbc4-4df2-9070-66fcfda1fa5a" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_1b3c3acd-9f26-4b6f-ac42-668c9e331cb7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> to at least one floor containing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_8067abad-b3bb-48af-a3ef-abf797214fd5" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy units</xref> and to the entrance doorway of each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_7aa54e79-a714-4c41-b474-312a3c867152" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> located on that level.</li><li>To and within not less than one of each type of room or space for use in common by the residents, including a cooking facility, sauna, gymnasium, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_227c45e8-bcda-4984-9cfa-b43b38e3d896" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, common laundry, games room, TV room, individual shop, dining room, public viewing area, ticket purchasing service, lunch room, lounge room, or the like.</li><li>Where a ramp complying with AS 1428.1 or a passenger lift is installed—<ol><li>to the entrance doorway of each <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_c5bbe2ac-11a2-4af3-90d4-3b0bdf65aa37" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref>; and</li><li>to and within rooms or spaces for use in common by the residents.</li></ol></li><li>The requirements of (iii) only apply where the space referred to in (iii)(A) or (iii)(B) is located on the levels served by the lift or ramp.</li></ol></li><li id="_b4882bb7-d108-4ae9-b3b8-7e83b0f61cb9"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_4517cbcd-8151-4f47-88ba-839988b3326e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Sole-occupancy units</xref> — to and within a number of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_124c027c-36b9-4438-bf58-786a20be93ea" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy units</xref> determined in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/37_1.4.0.xml#_118a8046-d884-4cc9-baa8-75574a067127" id="_75a2bf9b-364d-4efa-8548-cface1bd9004" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table D4D2b</xref>. </li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_a2dd582d-7dad-4e56-beb8-b33891ed655e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_22b9f525-ac92-42d0-9b20-a49f6f026014">SubClause</title><num>10</num><p>For a Class 10 building, access requirements are as follows:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_f4274e49-4729-42b8-a5d4-eb3656a4eb45">For a Class 10a non-habitable building located in an <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_38b3b867-c887-444d-98a9-798e4d545953" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> area intended for use by the public and containing a sanitary facility, change room facility or shelter, to and within—<ol><li>an <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_c086e0b9-223e-4c91-b11b-dd72c694ef0d" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> sanitary facility; and</li><li>a change room facility; and</li><li>a public shelter or the like.</li></ol></li><li id="_0bb7c4eb-f9a3-4ea7-8362-e859cf9a04a1">For Class 10b <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_986beeb2-c03a-4079-9fc4-f6a87f0b87b6" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pools</xref>, to and into <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_e5ba4cb5-7218-463e-91fe-a446b0c35caa" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pools</xref> with a total perimeter greater than 40 m, associated with a Class 1b, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 8 or 9 building that is <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_cd6c122c-70be-4680-a6a7-c9f53b42e7da" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_51e7bc3c-8279-4b83-8c1d-749708db95d9" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref>, but not <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_9bf0caaf-e8bf-48f6-8b67-9b5fd05126e8" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pools</xref> for the exclusive use of occupants of a Class 1b building or a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_fa32174c-0e5d-436e-b3a5-fa53c17543da" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> in a Class 2 or Class 3 building.</li></ol></subclause><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/34_1.1.0.xml" graph="None" id="_e1aaf424-bb3a-490a-b431-8aace1ebca04"><num/><title id="_8a92c25e-af70-498b-a4c5-7c2b37ee9570"/></table-reference><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/37_1.4.0.xml" graph="None" id="_118a8046-d884-4cc9-baa8-75574a067127"><num/><title id="_7ff390dd-de73-4694-b6ce-55a3d58bfd31"/></table-reference></clause>